author: quintonm
msg: - The errors instance variable is now a List.  The actual implementation used is ArrayList.
- renamed varDebug to debugVariables and changed it to a Map.
- deprecated getOut() since setOut() is deprecated.
- jndiContexts is now a Map instead of Hashtable
- deprecated getVarDebug().  The replacement is getDebugVariables().  I also added
setdebugVariable(name,value) so that people will have a way to use it.
